		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Your magic drains the magic from your target and slows their movement.</em></p><p><strong>Once Per Turn</strong> - 1 Creature (120 ft.) - 1 Minute - Magical</p><p><em>Trigger: You damage a creature who you have marked with Mark for Death.</em><br /></p><p><strong>[[/save constitution]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes 1d6 force damage*, their speed is halved, and they are &amp;reference[siphoned]. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Target takes 1d6 force damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p>*At level 11, this damage increases to 1d12.</p>",
